Package: rbcb
Type: Package
Title: R interface to Brazilian Central Bank web services
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Wilson Freitas <wilson.freitas@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Wilson Freitas <wilson.freitas@gmail.com>
Description: Brazilian Central Bank has an web interface with its systems of time series management.
    This package interfaces this systems through this web interface providing data in R's data structures.
